{"tid":1372884,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"國際特赦組織斥政府拒絕發不反對通知書圖製造更大混亂","createTime":"2019-07-27T14:01:22.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-27T19:16:08.000Z","uid":212626,"like":70,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"6541c1d09824154f604c2dd7f782383142b8f4bc","tid":1372884,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T14:01:22.000Z","msg":"今日警方在元朗集會中採用的武力，國際特赦組織香港分會在社交網站表示，政府拒絕發遊行不反對通知書以製造更大混亂，表明會動員各地分會，要求當地政府停止向特區政府供應「致命性較低」的人群管理裝備，直至港府成立獨立調查委員會徹查事件並作出具體改善。<br />\n<br />\n國際特赦組織香港分會又指，港人在國際法及《基本法》27條下可享有結社、集會、遊行示威自由，並指這種保障需要政府採取積極措施配合，包括製造有利環境讓市民行使權利，但政府不但拒絕發遊行不反對通知書，今天更在民居、店舖密集的地方施放催淚煙，試圖製造更多混亂。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1470864-20190727.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1470864-20190727.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=IcHW%2FfQ2zQNJFdNzTrXWKEuhYyo0AmqkWOXXUYRqYBI%3D&h=5f9797d8\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1470864-20190727.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=2ff5d746\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1470864-20190727.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"3099d92344ca267b452a937c522a457661798077","tid":1372884,"uid":212626,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T14:02:10.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\">表明會動員各地分會，要求當地政府停止向特區政府供應「致命性較低」的人群管理裝備，直至港府成立獨立調查委員會徹查事件並作出具體改善。</span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6214e95bd2f8dc5fb296bf46c0c6f2b3bfdb4928","tid":1372884,"uid":25169,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T14:03:09.000Z","msg":"[Online]關於撤退嘅問題<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1372554\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1372554</a>"},{"pid":"48121a7b722bac7b879888d78603fd0cc7aa77c0","tid":1372884,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-27T14:03:58.000Z","msg":"